 QMdnsEngine provides an implementation of multicast DNS as per RFC 6762,
 enabling Qt applications to provide mDNS services on the local network,
 respond to mDNS queries from other devices, and browse mDNS services provided
 by other devices on the local network.
 .
 This package contains the files necessary for development.

